    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings addressed, mitigating common platform weak points. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension setup. Presented in honest, driver-grade condition, this specimen offers a visceral, mechanically sound experience for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
