      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest signs of careful use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape; the premium upholstery shows light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, but the carpets and trim remain pristine. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust, backed by a comprehensive service log. It has recently undergone a full inspection, oil service, and brake check, ensuring it is ready for the road. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a dependable, clean, and thoroughly cared-for car for a discerning buyer.",
